SpaceCraft Resources — Notice on Derived Game Content
=====================================================

This repository contains two distinct kinds of material:

1. The `sc` tooling — the Python CLI, its tests, and the HTML/Vue
   inspectors under `src/public/`. This is original work authored for this
   project.

2. Generated release resources under `generated/` — item/recipe JSON,
   per-language translations, and recolored icons. These are DERIVED FROM
   the assets of the SpaceCraft game and therefore remain the intellectual
   property of the game's creators / publisher. They are reproduced here as
   an unofficial, non-commercial fan/community project.

This project is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by the makers
of SpaceCraft. All game names, trademarks, artwork, and game data are the
property of their respective owners. The generated resources are provided for
interoperability and community use only; if the rights holders object, they
will be removed on request.

Raw, unpacked game source is never committed to this repository (only the
`generated/` output is). See CLAUDE.md for details.
